        "text": "Genesis 23:9-17",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", could not come under this title—the field was Abraham’s purchase, not God’s gift as ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "κληρονομία",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " (see Meyer-Wendt, and Westcott, ",
